Sears - Wikipedia





















 






Sears

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Sears, Roebuck and Company)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the chain of department stores. For its parent company, see Sears Holdings. For other uses, see Sears (disambiguation).

Sears, Roebuck & Company





